{"data":[{"name":"69:1","price":"真灾，","arabic":"ٱلۡحَآقَّةُ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5324,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:2","price":"真灾是什么？","arabic":"مَا ٱلۡحَآقَّةُ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5325,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:3","price":"你怎么能认识真灾是什么呢？","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلۡحَآقَّةُ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5326,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:4","price":"赛莫德人和阿德人，曾否认大难。","arabic":"كَذَّبَتۡ ثَمُودُ وَعَادُۢ بِٱلۡقَارِعَةِ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5327,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:5","price":"至于赛莫德人呢，已为严刑所毁灭；","arabic":"فَأَمَّا ثَمُودُ فَأُهۡلِكُواْ بِٱلطَّاغِيَةِ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5328,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:6","price":"至于阿德人，已为怒吼的暴风所毁灭。","arabic":"وَأَمَّا عَادٞ فَأُهۡلِكُواْ بِرِيحٖ صَرۡصَرٍ عَاتِيَةٖ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5329,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:7","price":"他〔安拉〕曾使暴风对着他们连刮了七夜八昼，你看阿德人倒仆在地上，好像空心的海枣树干一样。","arabic":"سَخَّرَهَا عَلَيۡهِمۡ سَبۡعَ لَيَالٖ وَثَمَٰنِيَةَ أَيَّامٍ حُسُومٗاۖ فَتَرَى ٱلۡقَوۡمَ فِيهَا صَرۡعَىٰ كَأَنَّهُمۡ أَعۡجَازُ نَخۡلٍ خَاوِيَةٖ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5330,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:8","price":"你能看见他们还有孑遗吗？","arabic":"فَهَلۡ تَرَىٰ لَهُم مِّنۢ بَاقِيَةٖ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5331,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:9","price":"法老和在他之前的人，以及被倾覆的城市的居民，曾已铸成大错，","arabic":"وَجَآءَ فِرۡعَوۡنُ وَمَن قَبۡلَهُۥ وَٱلۡمُؤۡتَفِكَٰتُ بِٱلۡخَاطِئَةِ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5332,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:10","price":"他们曾违抗他们的养主的使者，故他严厉惩治了他们。","arabic":"فَعَصَوۡاْ رَسُولَ رَبِّهِمۡ فَأَخَذَهُمۡ أَخۡذَةٗ رَّابِيَةً","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5333,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:11","price":"当大水泛滥的时候，我让你们乘船，","arabic":"إِنَّا لَمَّا طَغَا ٱلۡمَآءُ حَمَلۡنَٰكُمۡ فِي ٱلۡجَارِيَةِ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5334,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:12","price":"以便我以那件事为你们的教训，以便能记忆的耳朵把它记住。","arabic":"لِنَجۡعَلَهَا لَكُمۡ تَذۡكِرَةٗ وَتَعِيَهَآ أُذُنٞ وَٰعِيَةٞ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5335,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:13","price":"当号角一响，","arabic":"فَإِذَا نُفِخَ فِي ٱلصُّورِ نَفۡخَةٞ وَٰحِدَةٞ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5336,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:14","price":"大地和山岳都被移动，且互相碰撞一次的时候；","arabic":"وَحُمِلَتِ ٱلۡأَرۡضُ وَٱلۡجِبَالُ فَدُكَّتَا دَكَّةٗ وَٰحِدَةٗ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5337,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:15","price":"在那日，那件大事将发生，","arabic":"فَيَوۡمَئِذٖ وَقَعَتِ ٱلۡوَاقِعَةُ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5338,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:16","price":"天将破裂；在那日，天将成为脆弱的。","arabic":"وَٱنشَقَّتِ ٱلسَّمَآءُ فَهِيَ يَوۡمَئِذٖ وَاهِيَةٞ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5339,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:17","price":"众天使将在天的各方；在那日，在他们上面，将有八个天使，担负你的养主的宝座；","arabic":"وَٱلۡمَلَكُ عَلَىٰٓ أَرۡجَآئِهَاۚ وَيَحۡمِلُ عَرۡشَ رَبِّكَ فَوۡقَهُمۡ يَوۡمَئِذٖ ثَمَٰنِيَةٞ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5340,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:18","price":"在那日，你们将被检阅，你们的任何秘密，都无法隐藏。","arabic":"يَوۡمَئِذٖ تُعۡرَضُونَ لَا تَخۡفَىٰ مِنكُمۡ خَافِيَةٞ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5341,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:19","price":"用右手接受自己的功过簿的人将说：“你们拿我的功过簿去读读吧！","arabic":"فَأَمَّا مَنۡ أُوتِيَ كِتَٰبَهُۥ بِيَمِينِهِۦ فَيَقُولُ هَآؤُمُ ٱقۡرَءُواْ كِتَٰبِيَهۡ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5342,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:20","price":"我确已猜想到我必遇见我的账目。”","arabic":"إِنِّي ظَنَنتُ أَنِّي مُلَٰقٍ حِسَابِيَهۡ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5343,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:21","price":"他将在愉快的生活里，","arabic":"فَهُوَ فِي عِيشَةٖ رَّاضِيَةٖ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5344,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:22","price":"在崇高的乐园里，","arabic":"فِي جَنَّةٍ عَالِيَةٖ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5345,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:23","price":"那里面的水果伸手可得。","arabic":"قُطُوفُهَا دَانِيَةٞ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5346,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:24","price":"“你们可以愉快地饮食，因为你们在过去的岁月中行过善。”","arabic":"كُلُواْ وَٱشۡرَبُواْ هَنِيٓـَٔۢا بِمَآ أَسۡلَفۡتُمۡ فِي ٱلۡأَيَّامِ ٱلۡخَالِيَةِ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5347,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:25","price":"以左手接过自己的功过簿的人将说：“啊呀！但愿我没有接过我的功过簿，","arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَنۡ أُوتِيَ كِتَٰبَهُۥ بِشِمَالِهِۦ فَيَقُولُ يَٰلَيۡتَنِي لَمۡ أُوتَ كِتَٰبِيَهۡ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5348,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:26","price":"不知道我自己的账目！","arabic":"وَلَمۡ أَدۡرِ مَا حِسَابِيَهۡ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5349,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:27","price":"但愿尘世的死亡已了结我的一生！","arabic":"يَٰلَيۡتَهَا كَانَتِ ٱلۡقَاضِيَةَ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5350,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:28","price":"我的财产于我毫无裨益，","arabic":"مَآ أَغۡنَىٰ عَنِّي مَالِيَهۡۜ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5351,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:29","price":"我的权柄已从我的手中消失。”","arabic":"هَلَكَ عَنِّي سُلۡطَٰنِيَهۡ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5352,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:30","price":"“你们捉住他，给他带上枷锁，","arabic":"خُذُوهُ فَغُلُّوهُ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5353,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:31","price":"然后把他投在烈火里，","arabic":"ثُمَّ ٱلۡجَحِيمَ صَلُّوهُ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5354,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:32","price":"然后把他穿在一条七十臂长的链子上。”","arabic":"ثُمَّ فِي سِلۡسِلَةٖ ذَرۡعُهَا سَبۡعُونَ ذِرَاعٗا فَٱسۡلُكُوهُ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5355,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:33","price":"他生前确是不信仰尊大的安拉，","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ كَانَ لَا يُؤۡمِنُ بِٱللَّهِ ٱلۡعَظِيمِ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5356,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:34","price":"不勉励人赈济贫民；","arabic":"وَلَا يَحُضُّ عَلَىٰ طَعَامِ ٱلۡمِسۡكِينِ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5357,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:35","price":"故今日他在这里没有一个亲戚。","arabic":"فَلَيۡسَ لَهُ ٱلۡيَوۡمَ هَٰهُنَا حَمِيمٞ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5358,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:36","price":"除脓汁外，他没有食物。","arabic":"وَلَا طَعَامٌ إِلَّا مِنۡ غِسۡلِينٖ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5359,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:37","price":"只有迷误的人们才吃脓汁。","arabic":"لَّا يَأۡكُلُهُۥٓ إِلَّا ٱلۡخَٰطِـُٔونَ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5360,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:38","price":"不然！我以你们所能见的万象盟誓，","arabic":"فَلَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِمَا تُبۡصِرُونَ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5361,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:39","price":"并且以你们所不能见的幽玄盟誓，","arabic":"وَمَا لَا تُبۡصِرُونَ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5362,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:40","price":"这确是尊贵的使者的言辞；","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ لَقَوۡلُ رَسُولٖ كَرِيمٖ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5363,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:41","price":"并不是诗人的言辞，你们很少信仰，","arabic":"وَمَا هُوَ بِقَوۡلِ شَاعِرٖۚ قَلِيلٗا مَّا تُؤۡمِنُونَ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5364,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:42","price":"也不是卜人的言辞，你们很少觉悟。","arabic":"وَلَا بِقَوۡلِ كَاهِنٖۚ قَلِيلٗا مَّا تَذَكَّرُونَ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5365,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:43","price":"这是从众世界的养主降示的。","arabic":"تَنزِيلٞ مِّن رَّبِّ ٱلۡعَٰلَمِينَ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5366,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:44","price":"假若他假借我的名义，捏造谣言，","arabic":"وَلَوۡ تَقَوَّلَ عَلَيۡنَا بَعۡضَ ٱلۡأَقَاوِيلِ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5367,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:45","price":"我必以权力逮捕他，","arabic":"لَأَخَذۡنَا مِنۡهُ بِٱلۡيَمِينِ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5368,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:46","price":"然后必割断他的大动脉，","arabic":"ثُمَّ لَقَطَعۡنَا مِنۡهُ ٱلۡوَتِينَ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5369,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:47","price":"你们中没有一个人能保卫他。","arabic":"فَمَا مِنكُم مِّنۡ أَحَدٍ عَنۡهُ حَٰجِزِينَ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5370,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:48","price":"这确是对敬畏者的教训。","arabic":"وَإِنَّهُۥ لَتَذۡكِرَةٞ لِّلۡمُتَّقِينَ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5371,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:49","price":"我的确知道你们中有否认的人。","arabic":"وَإِنَّا لَنَعۡلَمُ أَنَّ مِنكُم مُّكَذِّبِينَ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5372,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:50","price":"这对于不归信的人们确是悔恨。","arabic":"وَإِنَّهُۥ لَحَسۡرَةٌ عَلَى ٱلۡكَٰفِرِينَ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5373,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:51","price":"这确是真实的信念，","arabic":"وَإِنَّهُۥ لَحَقُّ ٱلۡيَقِينِ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5374,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"69:52","price":"故你当颂扬你的养主的大名。","arabic":"فَسَبِّحۡ بِٱسۡمِ رَبِّكَ ٱلۡعَظِيمِ","category":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah"],"ayahNumber":5375,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"}],"chapter":["69 (Al-Haqqah)","Al-Haqqah","Surah Al-Haqqah","Chapter Al-Haqqah","Haqqah","Surah Haqqah","Chapter Haqqah","Al Haqqah","Surah Al Haqqah","Chapter Al Haqqah","Surah 69","Chapter 69","The Reality","الحاقة"]}